data.description: Attention all ocean, lake, nature trail, bird watcher, canoe and kayak lovers!  This updated ranch style (POOL HOME) is located only minutes from the beach (with NO rear neighbors) and across the street from a nature park!  Once you have had your fill of the outdoors, you can retreat to this 3 bed 2 full bath charmer with an open floor plan, real wood floors (NO CARPET) vaulted ceilings with wood beams, a wood burning fireplace, large dining area and laundry room. Three sets of French doors lead out to your private pool deck great for relaxing and large enough for entertaining.  This home (is pre-wired for a generator) and even comes with a 28’ airstream which sleeps 4 and has AC, shower, bathroom (all hooked up to the public utilities) great for use at the pool, for kids’ sleepovers or for family gatherings/guest overflow. Best of all there is NO HOA and the complete house is covered with a bumper to bumper HOME WARRANTY!   Come see it today!
